thread.title: DANIEL
thread.title_full: Redspot Car Rentals reviewed by DANIEL

author: DANIEL
title: DANIEL
text:
All too easy, short walk to terminal. First getting the car was a bit slow so an extra staffer there would help but I was in no hurry 'this time'
Car was clean and comfortable. Was a small economy car so had no cruise control that I found worrying on the highway with speed cameras... my only gripe with car.
